content.task: Conduct comprehensive code review analysis to identify orphaned code, stub implementations, and duplicate code in the Stellar Hummingbot Connector v3.0 codebase. Focus on the main connector files in hummingbot/connector/exchange/stellar/ and related test files. Provide systematic identification framework and quality assessment.
content.context:
Code Quality Assessment Request:
- Target: Identify orphaned, stub, and duplicate code
- Scope: hummingbot/connector/exchange/stellar/ (40 Python modules) + test files
- Goal: Improve code maintainability and reduce technical debt
- Compliance: Must follow DEVELOPMENT_RULES.md (NEVER skip failing tests)
- Quality Standards: Apply qa/quality_catalogue.yml requirements
- Expected Output: Structured analysis with specific file/line references and remediation priorities
